name: Laberynth Horror
description:
Game title: Laberynth Horror.

Laberynth Horror is a horror game in which you find yourself in a labyrinth and you have to find the way out.

and you have to find the exit. On the way you will have to dodge the enemies and find 

enemies and find 5 keys to be able to open doors and thus be able to pass the level until you find the 

level until you find the exit.
